        {
            "title": "三星加速HBM4E開發 最快下月向英偉達送樣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X5Y0xwp7iLG7ukPTrtr0EQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC9D0FS_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據南韓媒體週四報導,三星電子 (KS:005930) 正在加速開發其下一代高頻寬記憶體(HBM4E)產品,以便最快於下月向英偉達 (NASDAQ:NVDA) 送出樣品。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據南韓媒體《朝鮮日報》引述業界消息人士報導,三星的目標是最快於下月生產出符合英偉達標準的首個HBM4E樣品。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星是同業中首家開始量產HBM4的公司,目前正在努力保持其在下一代記憶體領域的領先地位。三星曾於3月在英偉達年度開發者大會上展示了HBM4E實體樣品,但《朝鮮日報》的報導指出,該產品僅為展示用樣品。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ed739708-7cd3-318c-b6f2-933ddd61f2b6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">HBM是先進人工智能處理器的關鍵組件,三星從人工智能產業對記憶體的龐大需求中獲益良多。該公司是全球最大的記憶體晶片製造商,也是英偉達的主要供應商。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星在量產HBM4記憶體方面大幅領先SK海力士 (KS:000660) 和美光科技 (NASDAQ:MU),儘管這兩家公司近幾個月來被視為正在迅速追趕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於人工智能需求激增也引發了該板塊的供應短缺,記憶體晶片製造商從晶片價格飆升中獲益匪淺。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
